        <mxCell id="adr-ref" value="결정 근거 (docs/changes/):&#10;0005 워크스트림 A/B 분리   0006 SPA (Vite + S3/CloudFront)   0008 Cognito Self sign-up Disabled / MFA Required&#10;0009 S3 단일 bucket aegis-bucket-data + raw/processed/reports prefix   0010 Gabia 신규 도메인 + Route53 위임&#10;0012 Dashboard Backend = ECS Fargate (0007 Dashboard API 부분 + 0011 NAT GW 제거 supersede)&#10;0013 Aurora superseded → 0017 RDS PostgreSQL   0014 ElastiCache Redis (캐시 + Pub/Sub)&#10;0015 WebSocket + DynamoDB Streams   0016 Bedrock Claude 3 Haiku 일간 보고서&#10;로드맵: docs/planning/17_expansion_roadmap.md   Phase 1 통합 + Phase 2~4 트리거 표" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;fillColor=#FAFAFA;strokeColor=#616161;" vertex="1" parent="1">
